# - Try to find EPIX XCLIB
# Once done this will define
#
#  XCLIB_FOUND - system has EPIX XCLIB
#  XCLIB_INCLUDE_DIR - the EPIX XCLIB include directory
#  XCLIB_LIBRARIES - the libraries needed to use EPIX XCLIB
